# PR Review Tasks

## Mandatory First Step

Before performing ANY task, you MUST read the mandatory documentation. Do NOT skip this step. Do not guess conventions.

**MUST READ:**

- `docs/PR_REVIEW.md`
- `docs/PATTERN.md`

## Workflow

Gather PR info, analyze changes against architecture pattern rules, draft comments, approve/request changes via `gh` CLI as documented in `docs/PR_REVIEW.md`.
